io.sphere.sdk.categories

Interface Category

  • All Superinterfaces:
    CreationTimestamped, Custom, Identifiable<Category>, MetaAttributes, Referenceable<Category>, Resource<Category>, ResourceIdentifiable<Category>, ResourceView<Category,Category>, Timestamped, Versioned<Category>, WithLocalizedSlug

    public interface Category
extends Resource<Category>, WithLocalizedSlug, MetaAttributes, Custom
    Categories are used to organize products in a hierarchical structure.

    A category can have custom fields.

    Operations:

    • Create a category with CategoryCreateCommand.
    • Update a category with CategoryUpdateCommand.
    • Delete a category with CategoryDeleteCommand.

    Consult the documentation for categories for more information.
